    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/b432bbafda32bd2f20326079e4dbaab9.avif?t=1753152087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras_big/b432bbafda32bd2f20326079e4dbaab9.avif?t=1753152087 width=800 height=174 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/da0885c0934b7c75bdcbbea610867140.poster.avif?t=1753152087\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/da0885c0934b7c75bdcbbea610867140.webm?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/da0885c0934b7c75bdcbbea610867140.mp4?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瓦伦蒂娜是一名强大的女巫，也是最后一个可以操纵地狱之力的存在，她可以操纵无与伦比的力量与恶魔作战亦或者...杀戮无辜。末日即将到来，恶魔横行于世，信众对神的祈祷却丝毫得不到回应，但是信仰并没有由此消失，而是变得更加狂热，女巫审判成为了人类苦难的宣泄口。无数无辜的女性在熊熊燃烧的十字架上哭号，只有她，瓦伦蒂娜，无悲无喜的看着这些愚昧的信众。<strong><u>而你，纯洁的修士约翰</u></strong>，在神父的带领下与最后的女巫瓦伦蒂娜结下契约，只有维持处子之身才能维持这份人性的枷锁，让女巫暂时为人类而战。你的意识将永远与女巫相连，沉浸在同一片潜意识之海中......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/a7e7ce27569a88be71ab11e92aa49c6c.avif?t=1753152087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras_big/a7e7ce27569a88be71ab11e92aa49c6c.avif?t=1753152087 width=800 height=174 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/aa26cf2b073f7b5f64828157e42eac39.poster.avif?t=1753152087\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/aa26cf2b073f7b5f64828157e42eac39.webm?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/aa26cf2b073f7b5f64828157e42eac39.mp4?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个关卡都会有村民被选为守夜者，他们会增强建筑的效果，有一些还会有特殊的能力，或为你的军队提供自毁毒伤，或为你的箭塔提供火焰伤害，为您的战斗提供莫大的助力。在派遣界面合理分配他们驻守的建筑，会让您的防守计划更加完善。瓦伦蒂娜还可以通过献祭这些分配完成的村民释放威力强大的魔法，快速击杀整个地图的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/cddbdd48bd5f8dd72cfab1e5d6f412cf.avif?t=1753152087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras_big/cddbdd48bd5f8dd72cfab1e5d6f412cf.avif?t=1753152087 width=800 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/86fd920286ea76f06cbc7a2df99fe7d8.poster.avif?t=1753152087\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/86fd920286ea76f06cbc7a2df99fe7d8.webm?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/86fd920286ea76f06cbc7a2df99fe7d8.mp4?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在建筑崩溃之时，这些村民会无助的溃逃，也许会被恶魔宰杀......与其被怪物杀戮，不如由自己献祭？抑或是良心发现护送他们回到安全的地方？一切由你抉择，每一位守夜者都有自己的人生轨迹与结局，你决定会影响他们的命运......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/dd831ebc73efab6ac1fca19a4995e805.avif?t=1753152087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras_big/dd831ebc73efab6ac1fca19a4995e805.avif?t=1753152087 width=800 height=174 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/0fcb94f8e72b26c6eebcaa5c433a5658.poster.avif?t=1753152087\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/0fcb94f8e72b26c6eebcaa5c433a5658.webm?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/0fcb94f8e72b26c6eebcaa5c433a5658.mp4?t=1753152087\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以为魔女搭配主动技能、被动技能、你可以选择献祭村民生命产生的强力效果，你可以选择建筑物的升级路线以及附加的效果，你还可以决定兵营内产生的士兵种类、士兵升级后增强的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种选择相互之间会产生连锁反应，达到1+1大于2的效果。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>说了这么多，你敢接受挑战吗？</i> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于我们</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是一个小小小团队，想要跟我们保持联系，还请关注我们的社交媒体账号！（谢谢）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【社交媒体账号】 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras/2a76c86f7df5113e00c4e70961e749d3.avif?t=1753152087\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034180/extras_big/2a76c86f7df5113e00c4e70961e749d3.avif?t=1753152087 width=800 height=393 /></span></p>",
